page_content: The page discusses a colorectal cancer early detection program in the Canton of Fribourg.
The page provides information for individuals interested in renting a subsidized apartment.
The page provides information on how employers can issue salary statements, including the use of a specific software program for this purpose.
The page introduces an app called FunDent designed to promote good oral hygiene among children aged 4 to 12.
The page discusses the regular monitoring of water quality in public swimming and beach pools in the Canton of Fribourg.
The page discusses the construction progress of the Interkantonales Gymnasium der Region Broye, a joint project between the cantons of Fribourg and Vaud.
The page provides information on import and export regulations for food, living animals, and other goods of animal origin.
The page discusses a new system for managing parking permits at various locations and provides forms for parking permit requests for 2023-2024.
The page provides information and documents related to the harmonization of the personal registry in the Canton of Fribourg, including guides for the new AHV number (AHVN13).
The page provides general guidance on tax-related topics for individuals, such as self-employment, assets abroad, and withholding tax.
The content of the page could not be retrieved for analysis.
